hút Tô Cửu gia nhập tông môn mình mà tạm thời đạt thành giao kèo, cùng dạy dỗ Tô Cửu tu luyện. Ai ngờ, tu vi của Tô Cửu sở hữu \"Tinh Nguyên\" tiến bộ nhanh chóng, vượt xa tưởng tượng của hai cô gái.</p>","tmdb_id":207020,"cast":["Han Mo","Zhixiao Liu","Zhenxiu Su","Xin Zhao","Yuantao Zhang","Li Jiaxiang"],"director":[],"keywords":[],"tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"207020","season":1,"vote_average":7,"vote_count":1},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Han Mo","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Han Mo","tmdb_id":2368846,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/6Ueom0Y4pjIG9B6zjQlfIbgcGhH.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2368846"},{"name":"Zhixiao Liu","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zhixiao Liu","tmdb_id":2721285,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/hTtyU25PS0ZwLGwedFUzNBvJf4M.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2721285"},{"name":"Zhenxiu Su","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Zhenxiu Su","tmdb_id":3846987,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7JEtTPztbAKlot0J4lzAvahdXl3.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3846987"},{"name":"Xin Zhao","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Xin Zhao","tmdb_id":3846990,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/sUaiEZ6OyTJThvIhhpaHk5giOLa.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3846990"},{"name":"Yuantao Zhang","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Yuantao Zhang","tmdb_id":3912396,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/uzOe4jzS0nkZ7o9Hlx8QwqcArGc.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3912396"},{"name":"Li Jiaxiang","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Li Jiaxiang","tmdb_id":5477857,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/zAfsDoUPvbIoJ5s2T2Mj00ay5uN.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/5477857"}],"tmdb_checked":true,"pubjs_url":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/phantruongngoc102/pjs102@main/pubjs/ti/tinh-nguyen-chi-chu.json"}